        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To reduce Ben2 cost, focus on optimizing API calls. Implement batch processing where possible, cache frequent requests, and use efficient data serialization formats. For instance, compressing payloads can lower data transfer costs, and setting appropriate timeouts prevents unnecessary compute usage."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
